WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.897
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.120 --> 01:37.776
=Episode 2=

01:38.224 --> 01:44.016
(Two months ago)

01:54.032 --> 01:56.631
My Lady, when are we leaving?

01:57.312 --> 01:59.392
With no money, we can't go anywhere.

02:00.872 --> 02:01.791
Then what should we do?

02:03.791 --> 02:07.511
One, two, three, four.

02:08.551 --> 02:09.592
All done!

02:12.032 --> 02:12.951
Go wait over there.

02:12.951 --> 02:13.752
What about you?

02:14.472 --> 02:15.391
I'll think of a way.

02:16.071 --> 02:16.872
To get the money.

02:31.831 --> 02:32.976
Lady Ye,

02:33.152 --> 02:35.071
we were only told
to get you out of the mountain.

02:35.071 --> 02:37.351
We're not obligated to pay
for your upcoming journey.

02:39.752 --> 02:40.511
A carriage's here.

02:41.231 --> 02:43.111
Just give me a few coppers,
so I can leave.

02:43.432 --> 02:45.391
If I leave, you'll finally
have some peace.

02:46.071 --> 02:48.511
By imperial order,
you're to marry in the capital.

02:48.551 --> 02:50.312
You're heading for a good life.

02:50.312 --> 02:52.752
Why hassle common folks like us?

02:52.752 --> 02:53.551
Exactly.

02:53.551 --> 02:54.951
I never meant to hassle you.

02:55.312 --> 02:57.551
I just can't leave because I'm broke.

03:02.192 --> 03:04.592
If you don't send me off,
I'll have to stay right here

03:04.791 --> 03:07.071
to keep you gentlemen company
for the days to come.

03:07.951 --> 03:08.511
Lady Ye...

03:11.432 --> 03:12.032
Hurry!

03:12.511 --> 03:13.631
Give some coins to Lady Ye.

03:15.712 --> 03:16.472
Hurry up!

03:17.511 --> 03:19.824
Farewell! I'll come back
to visit you someday.

03:22.592 --> 03:23.671
So much money?

03:24.368 --> 03:27.032
(Changxing Gate)

03:27.032 --> 03:29.912
Young Lady, where are we heading
after we enter the city?

03:31.472 --> 03:33.032
Do you know Prince Ding's Mansion?

03:33.631 --> 03:34.351
I do.

03:34.992 --> 03:35.831
Sit tight.

03:57.992 --> 03:58.951
Young Lady,

03:59.472 --> 04:01.712
have a bowl of tea first
and take a load off.

04:02.432 --> 04:03.592
Do you serve pastries?

04:04.272 --> 04:05.032
Sure, we do.

04:06.872 --> 04:09.871
We have sesame cakes, blossom cakes,
osmanthus honey cakes,

04:10.032 --> 04:11.072
and seasonal fruits.

04:11.311 --> 04:13.592
Then I'll have a bowl of almond congee

04:13.791 --> 04:14.751
and some honey cakes.

04:15.551 --> 04:16.072
Right away!

04:17.632 --> 04:18.392
Enjoy your meal.

04:18.472 --> 04:19.152
Thank you.

04:20.152 --> 04:20.952
My Lady.

04:24.472 --> 04:25.272
Have some too.

04:25.472 --> 04:26.512
I'm not hungry. You eat.

04:36.991 --> 04:38.592
Prince Ding's Mansion is so quiet now.

04:41.952 --> 04:43.832
You haven't been back
in a long time, have you?

04:44.751 --> 04:46.431
Being quiet is already the best.

04:47.072 --> 04:49.791
(People used to show up
and make trouble years ago,)

04:50.632 --> 04:52.351
(nearly driving me out of business.)

04:52.392 --> 04:53.712
Make trouble? Why?

04:54.912 --> 04:55.791
You don't know?

04:56.464 --> 04:57.832
(Mo Xiuwen, Former Prince Ding)
Eight years ago,

04:57.832 --> 05:00.560
Prince Ding's brother, Mo Xiuwen,
brought troops back unapproved,

05:01.032 --> 05:03.191
giving the Cangbei invaders
the perfect opening,

05:03.392 --> 05:04.671
causing three cities to fall.

05:05.351 --> 05:08.472
With so many casualties,
how could they not hate him?

05:08.952 --> 05:11.592
(Death)
The court was furious and killed him.

05:13.392 --> 05:13.952
I know.

05:24.272 --> 05:26.320
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

05:31.072 --> 05:32.431
Is Mo Xiuyao doing well?

05:32.952 --> 05:34.231
Could he be well?

05:34.912 --> 05:36.336
Though he wasn't implicated,

05:36.712 --> 05:39.592
fighting the Cangbei invaders
cost him his legs.

05:40.351 --> 05:42.671
We hardly ever see him
out and about anymore.

05:43.991 --> 05:46.311
He was such a smart
and lively boy as a child,

05:46.952 --> 05:48.431
always coming by my stall

05:48.551 --> 05:49.832
to buy these honey cakes.

05:51.152 --> 05:52.072
Now...

05:53.136 --> 05:53.671
(Death)

05:53.671 --> 05:54.632
My mom said

05:54.960 --> 05:56.752
(Young Ye Li)
that Lishan Academy owes you.

05:57.551 --> 05:58.871
We'll try to make amends.

06:09.032 --> 06:09.991
(Mo Xiuyao,)

06:11.032 --> 06:11.991
(I left the mountain.)

06:13.351 --> 06:15.111
(For what my mom owes your family,)

06:16.231 --> 06:17.191
(I shall repay it.)

06:17.616 --> 06:21.712
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

06:33.592 --> 06:35.111
(The world holds two kinds of people,)

06:35.871 --> 06:38.392
(those who live in the mountains
and those who dwell below.)

06:39.472 --> 06:41.152
(The former don't wear caps.)

06:41.832 --> 06:44.832
(A simple thread to tie back
their hair brings them comfort.)

06:46.072 --> 06:47.832
(And the latter are different.)

06:48.272 --> 06:50.592
(They always wear
different styles of caps,)

06:51.311 --> 06:53.952
(each one serving
as a subtle constraint,)

06:54.311 --> 06:55.728
(presenting their status)

06:56.141 --> 06:58.191
(while also binding your steps.)

07:01.431 --> 07:02.032
Your Highness.

07:04.176 --> 07:04.871
Come in.

07:08.432 --> 07:09.328
- Your Highness.
- Your Highness.

07:19.912 --> 07:21.392
I'm not used to wearing a crown.

07:22.231 --> 07:23.311
Your Highness,

07:23.712 --> 07:25.552
you are to see Ms. Wen shortly.

07:25.732 --> 07:27.311
It wouldn't do to neglect your manners.

07:34.912 --> 07:37.632
Your Highness, we must hurry
with your dressing.

07:52.912 --> 07:53.512
Ow!

07:53.551 --> 07:55.991
Forgive me, Your Highness.
I'll be gentler.

08:05.008 --> 08:07.072
(Double Happiness)

08:07.072 --> 08:09.592
(I never cared for crowns,
nor any kind of cap.)

08:10.392 --> 08:11.311
(But now)

08:13.991 --> 08:14.991
(I've left the mountain.)

08:22.832 --> 08:24.711
Where did His Highness stay last night?

08:25.071 --> 08:28.791
His Highness usually rests
in his own chambers.

08:28.791 --> 08:30.471
He spent last night at the study.

08:42.431 --> 08:43.392
Your Highness,

08:43.831 --> 08:46.551
Ms. Wen caught a chill
last night and is unwell.

08:46.831 --> 08:48.671
She won't be able to see you today.

08:49.951 --> 08:50.671
She's ill?

08:51.632 --> 08:52.711
I shall go visit her then.

08:52.912 --> 08:54.191
A physician has seen her.

08:54.311 --> 08:56.191
It's better to let her rest undisturbed.

08:56.671 --> 08:58.992
She said she wouldn't
want her illness to affect you.

09:07.056 --> 09:09.456
(Sacred Tablet
of Late Husband, Mo Xiuwen)

09:12.912 --> 09:14.152
Mother, why won't you see her?

09:17.191 --> 09:18.112
I don't want to.

09:19.232 --> 09:21.191
I don't even know what to say.

09:23.872 --> 09:25.912
Later, go offer incense for your father.

09:27.671 --> 09:29.831
Ms. Wen, you've been kneeling
for a long time.

09:29.992 --> 09:31.071
Rise and rest awhile.

09:39.831 --> 09:41.551
Usually, I pay little attention to you.

09:42.551 --> 09:44.071
Is your birthday approaching?

09:45.591 --> 09:48.752
If you require anything additional,
tell the mansion beforehand.

09:57.671 --> 09:59.671
My birthday has already
passed this year.

10:05.272 --> 10:06.791
How has your recent study been?

10:07.056 --> 10:09.071
Is Tutor Song teaching diligently?

10:09.392 --> 10:11.232
Tutor Song left a year ago.

10:12.671 --> 10:13.551
He left?

10:14.071 --> 10:16.471
A year ago,
Tutor Song's mom passed away.

10:16.471 --> 10:18.671
He went home to mourn her death
and left his position.

10:19.551 --> 10:20.912
I didn't know that.

10:23.191 --> 10:26.591
Indeed, life is ephemeral,
and fate is never certain.

10:27.071 --> 10:30.032
Back then, you gave him twenty strings
of cash and several winter robes.

10:33.071 --> 10:33.872
Is that so?

10:35.471 --> 10:36.671
Perhaps...

10:37.912 --> 10:40.272
Perhaps it's because I grow older.

10:42.152 --> 10:44.392
My memory grows weaker.

10:45.591 --> 10:47.471
Truly, life is adrift

10:48.591 --> 10:50.232
and barely holds any certainty.

10:50.791 --> 10:53.831
Mom, I have studies to attend to.
I must take my leave.

11:00.831 --> 11:04.032
Ms. Wen, you're always so melancholy.
It harms your health.

11:04.311 --> 11:05.471
In my days to come,

11:06.431 --> 11:07.791
what joy could there possibly be?

11:12.032 --> 11:14.431
And him? Has he returned?

11:14.791 --> 11:15.984
It will take some time.

11:16.624 --> 11:17.680
He will definitely return.

11:18.392 --> 11:19.912
Please wait patiently.

11:21.872 --> 11:23.272
It's time to take your medicine.

11:39.216 --> 11:43.024
(Tuisi Pavilion)

11:53.191 --> 11:53.791
Your Highness.

11:55.431 --> 11:56.752
It's already this late.

11:56.752 --> 11:58.512
His Highness probably won't be coming.

11:58.671 --> 12:00.512
Spare your eyes and rest early.

12:02.752 --> 12:04.671
Alright, I'll rest.

12:40.752 --> 12:41.352
Your Highness?

12:42.671 --> 12:44.632
It's nothing. Go to sleep.

12:45.632 --> 12:46.232
Yes.

12:59.551 --> 13:00.831
Didn't I say it was nothing?

13:04.032 --> 13:05.352
My Lady, it's me.

13:08.791 --> 13:11.032
Why come to my room instead of sleeping?

13:13.191 --> 13:16.191
Suddenly being moved
to a new place feels strange.

13:16.951 --> 13:20.112
Prince Ding's Mansion is so large.
I don't know anyone.

13:20.551 --> 13:21.808
So, I'm a little frightened.

13:22.791 --> 13:25.071
I fear His Highness doesn't like us.

13:25.352 --> 13:27.471
I fear others in the mansion
don't like us.

13:28.551 --> 13:30.951
I fear we'll be sent back.

13:32.551 --> 13:33.551
Don't overthink it.

13:35.992 --> 13:37.872
His Highness likely won't come tonight.

13:37.992 --> 13:38.992
Sleep here with me.

13:39.392 --> 13:39.992
Alright.

13:47.951 --> 13:50.311
If we share the bed,
you won't fear anymore, right?

13:51.032 --> 13:52.471
With two of us, I fear no more.

13:53.071 --> 13:54.992
My Lady, what shall we do tomorrow?

13:57.791 --> 13:58.671
Tomorrow

13:59.471 --> 14:01.872
we shall go out for a walk
and look around

14:02.232 --> 14:04.112
to know the people
of Prince Ding's Mansion.

14:04.791 --> 14:05.431
What else?

14:07.951 --> 14:09.471
Organize our belongings,

14:10.512 --> 14:11.791
tidy up the courtyard,

14:12.311 --> 14:14.272
place a tea table before the gate,

14:15.232 --> 14:18.191
and put Mengding Shihua
and Guzhu Zisun tea on it.

14:19.071 --> 14:20.400
That way, on clear days,

14:20.400 --> 14:22.392
we can brew Mengding Shihua tea.

14:22.791 --> 14:25.311
And if it rains,
we'll brew the Guzhu Zisun tea.

14:27.632 --> 14:28.191
And what else?

14:29.791 --> 14:30.311
Nothing more.

14:30.872 --> 14:32.152
We only have one day.

14:32.992 --> 14:34.800
As for the many other things
I'd like to do,

14:35.088 --> 14:36.191
we can save them for later.

14:46.632 --> 14:48.152
Aren't Her Highness's plants

14:49.512 --> 14:50.831
merely some stones?

14:52.152 --> 14:55.112
Do you suppose they can truly bloom?

14:55.512 --> 14:57.831
Tao, Xing, quit the chatting.

14:57.831 --> 14:59.352
Fetch some pastries from the kitchen.

15:00.232 --> 15:01.352
- Yes.
- Yes.

15:08.912 --> 15:09.711
Your Highness,

15:10.352 --> 15:12.392
those were all the shops
your mom left to you.

15:12.591 --> 15:15.392
Those stewards moved funds
from the accounts in the morning,

15:15.471 --> 15:17.191
cooked the books in the afternoon,

15:17.512 --> 15:18.311
and then...

15:18.831 --> 15:21.191
and then had the old staff
sort everything out at night.

15:21.471 --> 15:23.591
Our people couldn't intervene at all.

15:29.711 --> 15:32.032
Aren't you anxious at all,
Your Highness?

15:33.352 --> 15:35.032
Let them scurry about for a few days.

15:36.632 --> 15:38.232
You are seriously carefree.

15:38.431 --> 15:40.311
Those are exceptionally valuable shops.

15:43.431 --> 15:44.032
Qingyu,

15:45.551 --> 15:46.791
where do you think he went?

15:48.752 --> 15:50.112
Who are you talking about?

15:51.912 --> 15:52.591
His Highness.

15:53.711 --> 15:55.352
I've been here for days now,

15:55.711 --> 15:57.311
but I've only seen him twice in total.

15:58.152 --> 16:00.152
Once was during the wedding ceremony,

16:00.551 --> 16:01.551
and the other time

16:01.872 --> 16:04.311
was when I bumped into him
during my morning exercise.

16:05.272 --> 16:06.512
We barely exchanged greetings.

16:07.872 --> 16:09.791
Why do I never get to see him?

16:10.191 --> 16:12.992
Would someone with trouble walking
leave the house so often?

16:13.791 --> 16:15.872
He should have been
at home all this time.

16:15.912 --> 16:18.232
I notice he's been in the study
these past few days,

16:18.232 --> 16:20.352
with meals brought to him
on time every day.

16:20.951 --> 16:21.752
The study?

16:26.071 --> 16:27.232
Where are you going?

16:35.872 --> 16:36.551
Your Highness.

16:38.791 --> 16:39.912
Let me see His Highness.

16:40.071 --> 16:43.232
His Highness is preoccupied
and can't see visitors now.

16:44.912 --> 16:45.431
"Visitors"?

16:47.191 --> 16:49.711
This is Prince Ding's Mansion.
And I am Princess Ding.

16:50.232 --> 16:52.872
When I demand to see my husband,
I'm merely a 'visitor'?

16:53.352 --> 16:56.191
Please calm your anger.
I didn't mean that.

16:56.991 --> 16:59.072
But the Empress Dowager decreed it so.

16:59.431 --> 17:01.592
You and I dare not defy it, do we?

17:02.711 --> 17:03.471
Lord Lv.

17:04.552 --> 17:06.072
His Highness is a man of merit.

17:06.671 --> 17:09.191
Even if someone from this mansion
once took a wrong path,

17:09.431 --> 17:11.552
the Empress Dowager
and His Majesty don't blame him.

17:12.312 --> 17:13.991
As the Bureau of Astronomy's head,

17:14.352 --> 17:16.152
your acting on the so-called gods' word

17:16.632 --> 17:17.431
is rather improper.

17:22.312 --> 17:24.552
What a sharp tongue Your Highness has!

17:25.112 --> 17:27.951
It's a pity that I hold little weight.

17:28.271 --> 17:29.711
I am merely acting on orders.

17:30.312 --> 17:32.231
I cannot bear such a heavy accusation.

17:33.711 --> 17:35.912
This mansion carries
heavy sins of bloodshed,

17:36.392 --> 17:37.751
and calamities cling to it.

17:38.231 --> 17:39.352
I am here precisely

17:39.352 --> 17:41.832
to help the mansion ward off disaster
and absolve its sins.

17:41.832 --> 17:43.431
I hope Your Highness

17:43.632 --> 17:45.671
sees my sincere intention.

17:47.312 --> 17:47.912
Please.

17:56.152 --> 17:56.671
By the way,

17:58.271 --> 18:00.152
I heard you are from the south.

18:00.632 --> 18:01.951
How long have you been here?

18:08.552 --> 18:09.112
Three years.

18:10.431 --> 18:11.191
Three years?

18:12.031 --> 18:14.152
Then your court speech
is remarkably good.

18:14.592 --> 18:16.632
I assumed you grew up
right here in the capital.

18:27.431 --> 18:28.872
Do not be angry, Your Highness.

18:29.951 --> 18:30.792
I'm not angry.

18:31.792 --> 18:32.832
Have a carriage ready.

18:33.352 --> 18:34.392
Are you going out?

18:35.711 --> 18:36.271
Yes.

18:52.031 --> 18:53.231
What are they doing?

18:53.671 --> 18:54.471
Your Highness,

18:55.552 --> 18:56.711
it's the Soul-Awakening Bell.

18:56.951 --> 18:58.951
Sound flows through meridians,
so say the old.

18:59.312 --> 19:00.912
Striking the bell with metal and stone

19:01.008 --> 19:02.960
can help people regulate their meridians

19:03.228 --> 19:04.711
and rid them of ill luck.

19:05.271 --> 19:06.671
Please come with me.

19:08.951 --> 19:11.088
This tea was picked
around the Qingming Festival,

19:11.088 --> 19:12.552
while the dew was still fresh.

19:12.751 --> 19:15.632
The aroma of dew
lingers on the leaf buds.

19:15.832 --> 19:17.431
Hence its name, Dew Bud Spring.

19:17.711 --> 19:18.392
Try it.

19:20.352 --> 19:21.424
Thank you, Uncle Wenshen.

19:25.471 --> 19:26.152
Well?

19:29.711 --> 19:32.711
What brings you here to my place today?

19:33.392 --> 19:35.511
Is life at Prince Ding's Mansion
too leisurely?

19:36.552 --> 19:37.592
It's a wonderful place.

19:38.552 --> 19:40.991
His Highness and my sister-in-law
are both easy-going.

19:41.912 --> 19:43.671
I've been back
in the capital for a while.

19:43.991 --> 19:45.552
Paying my respects is right.

19:45.711 --> 19:47.832
And besides, at home the other day,

19:47.832 --> 19:49.592
you spoke on my behalf several times.

19:49.991 --> 19:51.511
I am deeply grateful.

19:53.511 --> 19:55.592
I don't get along with your father.

19:56.031 --> 19:57.191
I didn't do it just for you.

19:58.471 --> 20:01.191
Besides, with that skill of yours,

20:01.671 --> 20:03.912
can Ms. Wang really outsmart you?

20:05.431 --> 20:08.231
You could have walked away
unscathed even without me.

20:08.711 --> 20:10.031
Please don't say that.

20:11.152 --> 20:12.511
I was away for eight years,

20:12.792 --> 20:14.912
only to be rejected by Father
upon returning.

20:15.352 --> 20:18.031
In this sprawling capital,
I have no one else to rely on.

20:19.072 --> 20:21.271
Running this Longevity Shop,

20:21.751 --> 20:23.751
you're well-connected
with excellent sources.

20:24.112 --> 20:25.520
If I could gain your favor,

20:25.968 --> 20:27.352
I'd feel a bit more reassured.

20:28.152 --> 20:29.872
My mom always said before

20:30.072 --> 20:31.271
that you have

20:31.471 --> 20:33.951
a tongue as sharp as blades
but a heart as warm as spring,

20:34.511 --> 20:37.112
while possessing gallantry
worthy of Lord Mengchang,

20:37.632 --> 20:39.912
and if someday troubled times arise,

20:40.392 --> 20:42.471
seeking your help
is always the right choice.

20:49.751 --> 20:50.711
How is

20:52.552 --> 20:53.312
your mom?

21:02.872 --> 21:05.511
After all, it is our Ye family

21:05.792 --> 21:06.792
that has wronged her.

21:07.592 --> 21:09.471
Alright. What do you need my help with?

21:12.792 --> 21:14.392
There actually is one thing

21:15.431 --> 21:17.312
that I hope you can look into for me.

21:18.231 --> 21:19.352
Lv Cheng?

21:21.191 --> 21:21.991
Not familiar.

21:23.951 --> 21:27.312
I believe he previously served
as a registrar in Lianzhou.

21:29.552 --> 21:31.231
Just a tiny, insignificant post.

21:32.511 --> 21:35.031
Somehow he managed
to connect with Marquis Muyang

21:35.471 --> 21:37.271
and got to join the Bureau of Astronomy.

21:38.632 --> 21:39.832
The man knows how to maneuver.

21:40.312 --> 21:41.832
Marquis Muyang values him highly.

21:41.832 --> 21:43.471
His rise has been meteoric since.

21:44.872 --> 21:47.696
His hostility towards
Prince Ding's household

21:49.671 --> 21:52.080
must be on Marquis Muyang's orders.

21:55.231 --> 21:57.312
He never held office
in the capital before?

21:58.312 --> 21:59.112
Did he?

21:59.872 --> 22:00.872
I don't believe so.

22:02.792 --> 22:04.152
How are you handling this?

22:04.751 --> 22:06.431
This lamp is far too small.

22:06.431 --> 22:09.271
For blessings and prosperity,
of course bigger is better!

22:09.271 --> 22:10.031
Master.

22:10.031 --> 22:10.711
What is it?

22:11.832 --> 22:13.112
The wife of Lord Lv

22:13.112 --> 22:15.352
is complaining that our
ceremonial lamp is too small.

22:15.392 --> 22:16.511
She insists on changing it.

22:17.191 --> 22:19.271
Scorning a third-rank
official belt as too tight?

22:19.271 --> 22:19.912
Very well.

22:19.912 --> 22:22.152
She should go ask
for an imperial robe instead.

22:22.671 --> 22:25.352
This isn't the Imperial Seal Office
or a pawnshop.

22:25.632 --> 22:26.672
She finds the lamp small?

22:26.672 --> 22:27.872
I want the largest lamp!

22:28.031 --> 22:30.552
Let her ask her husband for it.
Why raise a fuss here?

22:30.592 --> 22:31.912
You're absolutely right.

22:32.632 --> 22:33.471
Lord Lv,

22:34.671 --> 22:35.352
Lv Cheng?

22:36.112 --> 22:37.104
Who else could it be?

22:38.152 --> 22:39.031
That is his wife.

22:39.511 --> 22:42.640
Our Lv family offers the lamp
for everyone's sake, of course.

22:42.872 --> 22:43.511
This spot...

22:43.511 --> 22:44.671
She will place her lamp here?

22:45.511 --> 22:47.951
She's choosing the lamp today
to light it tomorrow.

22:49.511 --> 22:50.312
Uncle Wenshen,

22:50.632 --> 22:52.872
I also wish to offer a lamp
for my husband.

22:53.392 --> 22:55.231
Certainly. When?

22:55.872 --> 22:56.711
Tomorrow.

22:57.296 --> 22:59.031
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

22:59.031 --> 23:00.912
I'll go to the Longevity Shop
again tomorrow.

23:01.231 --> 23:02.352
Prepare some offerings.

23:03.632 --> 23:04.312
Alright.

23:07.792 --> 23:08.592
Your Highness.

23:09.112 --> 23:10.448
Is His Highness in the study?

23:11.912 --> 23:13.231
His Highness now...

23:13.744 --> 23:14.671
Now...

23:17.832 --> 23:18.751
What's that sound?

23:20.832 --> 23:23.832
As you know, this mansion
suffered divine punishment,

23:24.312 --> 23:28.072
so every month Lord Lv
must conduct a purification ritual here

23:28.072 --> 23:30.152
to beseech heavenly protection.

23:30.312 --> 23:31.112
Divine punishment?

23:38.271 --> 23:41.231
Gods descend,

23:41.592 --> 23:43.471
repelling sins and calamity!

23:44.152 --> 23:46.288
Grant this mansion

23:46.384 --> 23:50.031
long and deep blessings!

23:50.896 --> 23:58.064
♪In silence, figures fade away♪

23:59.536 --> 24:03.472
♪Those fallen into the abyss♪

24:04.304 --> 24:08.935
♪Hold my life that hangs by a thread♪

24:10.655 --> 24:17.744
♪If you treat pain as swallowed needles♪

24:19.216 --> 24:29.623
♪The scars etched
sharpen the heart to a blade♪

24:31.031 --> 24:32.191
What are they burning?

24:32.431 --> 24:33.271
Scriptures.

24:33.431 --> 24:35.312
Copied daily by His Highness himself.

24:37.671 --> 24:38.320
Your Highness!

24:39.671 --> 24:41.031
Best not to cause interference.

24:49.648 --> 24:53.712
♪When falsehoods bow to command♪

24:54.552 --> 24:57.991
Repent!

24:59.408 --> 25:03.088
♪I would rather light a lamp♪

25:03.088 --> 25:11.664
♪Than be a vassal to a grand illusion♪

25:12.431 --> 25:14.592
Sins are laid bare.

25:18.511 --> 25:21.072
Faults are atoned for.

25:23.552 --> 25:25.392
Through sky-reaching sincerity,

25:28.072 --> 25:31.072
may Heaven perceive the pledge.

25:31.152 --> 25:35.088
♪Grant the living a glimmer of hope♪

25:36.112 --> 25:40.368
♪Ease the grief of the departed♪

25:40.976 --> 25:50.448
♪Follow me, debts unpaid, march on♪

25:50.800 --> 25:54.672
♪Cast into despair♪

25:55.728 --> 26:00.656
♪I search for a sliver of hope♪

26:00.688 --> 26:04.752
♪I would rather drain our hope♪

26:04.752 --> 26:15.472
♪Than survive temporarily for illusions♪

26:17.392 --> 26:18.392
Your Highness,

26:21.271 --> 26:22.711
let's conclude today's ritual.

26:23.271 --> 26:25.792
On the first day of next month,
my attendants and I

26:26.191 --> 26:27.392
will pay another visit.

26:33.751 --> 26:34.384
Your Highness.

27:04.872 --> 27:07.671
Your Highness, the wine jug is empty.
I'll go fetch another.

27:14.896 --> 27:23.471
(Jianquan Spring)

27:23.471 --> 27:24.304
I'm coming in.

27:39.711 --> 27:41.031
Who said you could enter?

27:41.991 --> 27:42.832
Leave.

27:46.072 --> 27:47.152
I announced myself.

27:48.511 --> 27:49.592
You did not respond.

27:50.191 --> 27:51.592
So I took it as consent.

28:46.951 --> 28:48.431
So eager to play a virtuous wife?

28:49.072 --> 28:51.832
There are ashes from the ritual
clinging to your hair.

28:52.271 --> 28:53.792
I merely wanted to clean it for you.

29:00.072 --> 29:02.031
Let me keep Your Highness company.

29:14.271 --> 29:17.152
Before this, I resided constantly
on Lishan Mountain.

29:18.152 --> 29:19.592
Suddenly moving somewhere new

29:19.751 --> 29:22.191
and settling into this mansion,
I still feel awkward.

29:23.872 --> 29:25.352
Lishan Mountain holds many flowers.

29:25.951 --> 29:27.344
This mansion has a garden too.

29:27.728 --> 29:29.271
But the flowers here don't look nice.

29:30.031 --> 29:31.632
It's better to make it a vegetable patch

29:31.951 --> 29:34.431
and plant leeks for making leek cakes.

29:34.471 --> 29:36.191
If this place ill suits you,
simply leave.

29:46.592 --> 29:47.471
On the mountain,

29:48.191 --> 29:50.711
if I craved something,
I had to grow it myself.

29:51.431 --> 29:53.031
I fetched drinking water from streams.

29:53.552 --> 29:56.191
Mischievous monkeys
would pilfer belongings.

29:56.991 --> 29:59.031
They also bite,
utterly detestable creatures.

30:25.951 --> 30:28.431
Every day, besides farming,

30:28.951 --> 30:30.832
I also had to study and attend classes.

30:31.711 --> 30:33.912
My grandfather and tutors
watched me closely.

30:34.711 --> 30:35.671
To be honest,

30:36.152 --> 30:37.471
I had more homework than you.

30:38.991 --> 30:40.632
Poetry, books, rites, music,

30:40.951 --> 30:44.072
arithmetic, astronomy,
and hydraulic engineering.

30:44.632 --> 30:46.072
The tutors taught everything,

30:46.431 --> 30:48.112
and gave mountains of homework daily.

30:50.072 --> 30:51.912
Your mansion has plenty of books too.

31:02.152 --> 31:03.984
I'd often bring
one or two volumes with me

31:04.082 --> 31:05.431
to read at the mountain top.

31:06.352 --> 31:08.792
If I got tired, I'd raise my head
and look at the sky.

31:10.872 --> 31:11.504
Look.

31:12.552 --> 31:14.951
The moon is bright
and clear tonight, halo-free.

31:15.592 --> 31:18.352
Altair, Vega, and nearby stars
shine brightly and clearly.

31:19.231 --> 31:21.711
Your Highness,
it will surely be sunny tomorrow.

31:22.751 --> 31:24.872
I don't care what tomorrow brings.

31:28.552 --> 31:29.471
Back on the mountain,

31:30.271 --> 31:31.781
I heard a lot

31:32.112 --> 31:33.511
about Your Highness.

31:36.152 --> 31:37.592
What happened back then was sudden.

31:37.872 --> 31:39.152
You didn't know about it.

31:39.231 --> 31:41.031
Not to mention your brother...

31:41.031 --> 31:42.112
Why say these things?

31:43.352 --> 31:43.991
Out of pity?

31:49.951 --> 31:52.312
Please leave, Ye Li. I don't need you.

32:09.471 --> 32:10.392
I just wanted to say

32:11.191 --> 32:12.431
I don't want to leave.

32:13.231 --> 32:15.951
Life at this mansion is still better
than living on the mountain.

32:17.511 --> 32:18.312
And,

32:19.511 --> 32:20.271
Mo Xiuyao,

32:21.392 --> 32:22.912
do you really not remember me?

32:25.392 --> 32:26.231
Your Highness.

32:28.392 --> 32:30.352
Your Highness, the wine is ready.

32:44.271 --> 32:45.392
(On our wedding day,)

32:45.711 --> 32:47.912
(I told him it was our first meeting.)

32:48.751 --> 32:50.031
(Actually, I was lying.)

32:51.671 --> 32:52.552
(He and I)

32:52.792 --> 32:56.072
(had already met a very long time ago.)

32:58.191 --> 32:59.632
(In the spring of Jinghe 13,)

33:00.191 --> 33:02.392
(Mom and I headed north
through Yanming Pass)

33:02.951 --> 33:05.072
(towards Fire Worship City
for the New Sun festival.)

33:06.152 --> 33:07.352
(Desert bandits attacked us.)

33:08.031 --> 33:09.232
(I got separated from Mom.)

33:10.072 --> 33:10.951
(It was right there)

33:11.792 --> 33:13.392
(that I first saw Mo Xiuyao.)

33:47.352 --> 33:50.912
(Afterward, I went around
asking people about him.)

33:51.431 --> 33:53.152
(I even thought of finding him at camp.)

33:53.751 --> 33:55.072
(Shame we never met again.)

33:56.392 --> 33:57.352
(I heard people say)

33:57.751 --> 34:00.392
(that he was a young prodigy,
full of vitality,)

34:00.832 --> 34:02.471
(really lively and outgoing.)

34:04.672 --> 34:06.192
(But to me back then,)

34:06.672 --> 34:09.591
(he was just a guy with great strength.)

34:10.832 --> 34:12.431
(But whichever version he was)

34:13.151 --> 34:16.272
(was much better than how he is now.)

34:38.392 --> 34:40.031
It's fine. You can go rest.

35:31.352 --> 35:39.888
- The Lu throw!
- The Lu throw!

35:39.888 --> 35:43.312
(Mo Yanqi, Emperor)
The Lu throw!

35:46.511 --> 35:48.991
Three black, two pheasants.
It's a Zhi throw.

35:48.991 --> 35:49.672
Your Majesty,

35:49.672 --> 35:50.591
please make your move.

35:51.151 --> 35:52.991
I'm sure to win this match.

35:59.352 --> 36:07.872
- The Lu throw!
- The Lu throw!

36:07.872 --> 36:09.272
The Empress Dowager has arrived!

36:09.272 --> 36:10.192
Lu!

36:14.872 --> 36:15.504
Mother.

36:15.664 --> 36:18.192
(Guo Jin, Empress Dowager)

36:18.192 --> 36:21.111
All servants present here
each take ten strikes!

36:21.111 --> 36:23.431
- Empress Dowager, spare us!
- Empress Dowager, spare us!

36:23.431 --> 36:24.551
- Your Majesty!
- Your Majesty!

36:24.551 --> 36:29.232
- Your Majesty, spare us!
- Your Majesty, spare us!

36:29.232 --> 36:30.151
Shut up.

36:31.632 --> 36:32.872
Receive your punishment.

36:33.392 --> 36:34.712
- Yes!
- Yes!

36:50.752 --> 36:52.272
Such a fine Peaceful Emperor!

36:52.912 --> 36:55.472
The three Fanzhen of Hebei
are falling behind on their tribute.

36:56.232 --> 36:58.672
The rebels in eastern Zhejiang
have seized four prefectures.

36:59.551 --> 37:01.272
Yet you still have the leisure

37:01.272 --> 37:03.111
to gamble in the hall.

37:04.071 --> 37:06.832
Don't forget. You are the emperor.

37:08.192 --> 37:08.752
Yes.

37:09.511 --> 37:10.431
I was wrong.

37:11.752 --> 37:14.591
As the ruler,
you should lead by example.

37:15.312 --> 37:18.111
But you allowed
your inner circle to gamble openly.

37:18.672 --> 37:21.232
You disrespect your late father
and the imperial court.

37:21.471 --> 37:23.344
How can you face your ancestors

37:23.344 --> 37:24.624
and your late father?

37:24.832 --> 37:26.192
How can you face the officials

37:26.192 --> 37:27.951
who diligently govern on your behalf?

37:32.511 --> 37:33.192
Emperor.

37:34.352 --> 37:35.071
'Emperor'?

37:37.752 --> 37:40.471
Do you truly want me
to be the Emperor, Mother?

37:42.352 --> 37:43.511
You are still young.

37:44.151 --> 37:46.832
The court's human relationships
are intricate.

37:47.312 --> 37:48.392
You can't control it yet.

37:50.352 --> 37:52.352
If it weren't for Lishan Academy
sealing its doors,

37:53.151 --> 37:55.151
you'd have likely ascended
to the throne long ago.

37:55.511 --> 37:57.991
Would I still have this chance
to listen to your guidance now?

38:29.072 --> 38:31.408
(Ji Lodge)

38:31.408 --> 38:36.272
(Vigilant From Dawn to Dusk)

38:36.272 --> 38:37.031
Your Highness.

38:38.951 --> 38:41.111
Lord Lv said no one enters here
without permission.

38:41.792 --> 38:42.712
Where is this place?

38:43.111 --> 38:44.631
It's... Prince Ding's Mansion.

38:45.951 --> 38:47.551
So you know it's Prince Ding's Mansion?

38:48.511 --> 38:49.712
By what right do you stop me?

38:52.031 --> 38:54.071
The Empress Dowager
only said to copy scriptures.

38:54.431 --> 38:56.991
She never ordered him
locked away with no visitors.

38:57.912 --> 38:59.471
He hasn't eaten for several days.

38:59.991 --> 39:02.712
If something happens to him,
can you bear the responsibility?

39:15.431 --> 39:16.352
I'm coming in.

39:24.312 --> 39:25.591
Eat something first.

39:28.151 --> 39:29.752
I made this especially for you.

39:30.471 --> 39:32.912
This bowl has millet porridge.
I added almonds.

39:33.192 --> 39:34.704
Good for your stomach and warms you.

39:35.672 --> 39:38.312
You haven't eaten in days.
You must be starving by now.

39:41.352 --> 39:42.431
Leave me alone.

39:50.792 --> 39:52.111
This room is too dark.

39:52.951 --> 39:54.071
It needs some light.

40:06.912 --> 40:09.352
After days locked away,
your complexion is poor.

40:10.792 --> 40:11.752
None of your concern.

40:15.712 --> 40:16.471
You're sick?

40:26.551 --> 40:27.591
You can feel pulses?

40:30.111 --> 40:32.071
I do more than feeling pulses
and diagnosing.

40:32.352 --> 40:33.591
I can even read fortunes too.

40:34.272 --> 40:37.071
Known as a reclusive master
of medicine who can raise the dead,

40:37.071 --> 40:38.151
Master Helai

40:38.352 --> 40:40.912
excels in medicine, divination,
and fortune-telling.

40:41.352 --> 40:43.551
I learned from him,
so I know medicine too.

40:44.912 --> 40:47.111
Mo Xiuyao, would you
like to give it a try?

40:55.792 --> 40:57.471
If you don't want an examination,

40:58.151 --> 40:59.192
let me tell your fortune.

41:05.071 --> 41:05.991
Your Highness,

41:06.912 --> 41:08.712
your brows meet the heavens.

41:09.752 --> 41:11.312
Your earlobes drop like pearls.

41:11.951 --> 41:14.752
Your eyes are like autumn water,
with no sign of ill fate.

41:15.752 --> 41:18.111
Your fate is not bound
by the Book of Life and Death.

41:19.312 --> 41:21.951
Your Highness has a great fate
and a long life.

41:22.752 --> 41:25.071
Fasting won't kill you. Eat something.

41:28.071 --> 41:29.151
A long life?

41:30.792 --> 41:32.352
A life where everyone around is gone,

41:35.071 --> 41:36.631
and I alone remain alive?

41:54.192 --> 41:56.551
I can do that too. Did I look like you?

42:09.631 --> 42:10.591
What are you doing now?

42:13.031 --> 42:13.951
Drink it hot.

42:22.912 --> 42:23.951
I'll leave after you eat.

42:39.664 --> 42:42.928
(Preview)

42:43.431 --> 42:46.232
Your Highness just doesn't
know me well enough yet.

42:47.192 --> 42:48.071
It doesn't matter.

42:48.431 --> 42:51.071
With some time,
we will naturally grow closer.

42:51.752 --> 42:53.352
Mrs. Lv just placed her lamp and left?

42:53.591 --> 42:54.591
Yes.

42:54.792 --> 42:57.272
She insisted on placing her lamp
on the highest stand.

42:57.551 --> 42:58.752
How was it settled in the end?

42:58.951 --> 43:01.151
(Lv Boying)
She put it in the second layer's center.

43:01.192 --> 43:03.792
Senior Eunuch Shunxi,
it's a misunderstanding!

43:03.856 --> 43:05.471
Senior Eunuch, it's a misunderstanding!

43:05.471 --> 43:07.151
Senior Eunuch, it's a misunderstanding!

43:07.151 --> 43:07.872
Senior Eunuch!

43:15.416 --> 43:22.008
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.592 --> 43:31.736
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:33.944 --> 43:37.176
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.400 --> 43:43.416
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:43.736 --> 43:47.160
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.224 --> 43:53.784
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:54.840 --> 43:58.776
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:58.776 --> 44:04.472
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:04.984 --> 44:13.592
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.488 --> 44:19.992
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:19.992 --> 44:25.496
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.560 --> 44:29.624
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:29.912 --> 44:35.136
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:35.736 --> 44:39.448
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.480 --> 44:45.144
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:45.912 --> 44:53.880
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.288 --> 45:00.536
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:00.792 --> 45:06.696
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:06.696 --> 45:10.816
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.032 --> 45:15.768
♪Unbound by form♪

45:16.984 --> 45:21.256
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.496 --> 45:26.936
♪Unbound by form♪
